# Web deployment optimization - exclude heavy files not needed at runtime

# API app entirely (not needed for web deployment)
apps/api/

# Git history is very heavy (57MB)
.git/

# Documentation and logs
*.md
*.log
docs/
README*

# Development files and caches
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.turbo/
**/coverage/
**/.next/cache/
**/node_modules/.cache/
**/.pnpm-store/

# Test files
**/__tests__/
**/*.test.*
**/*.spec.*
**/test/

# IDE files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store

# Source maps and dev configs (post-build optimization)
**/*.map
**/.eslintrc.*
**/.prettierrc*

# Heavy development dependencies that aren't needed at runtime
**/node_modules/@types/
**/node_modules/typescript/
**/node_modules/eslint/
**/node_modules/@typescript-eslint/
**/node_modules/prettier/
**/node_modules/@trivago/
**/node_modules/turbo/